imdb.plot outline: "LondonLove" follows the life of Annmarie Richa, star of the hit reality series "The Beautiques", and her newly-wed husband, Beshara, as they move to glitzy London from tropical Lebanon to start a business and a new life. The show follows their marriage and potential business opportunities developing while living in the glamorous and historical city of London, England.
